{"data": [{"id": "4741830", "title": "UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Stanley Black &amp; Decker, Inc. in conjunction with this event.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106009\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741830-ubs-global-industrials-and-transportation-conference", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:05:18"}, {"id": "4741817", "title": "Total Return Forecasts: Major Asset Classes - December 3, 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman is stacking coins\" data-id=\"183865137\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1006px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">acilo</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The long-term performance forecast for the Global Market Index (GMI) continued to increase in November, marking a full reversal of the recent slide in ex ante data. Today\u2019s estimate also marks the highest return outlook in recent history and is modestly above</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741817-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-december-3-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:00:00"}, {"id": "4741801", "title": "Energias de Portugal: Still Left Behind", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ribeira dilhas beach in Ericeira with turquoise water on a sunny day, in Portugal\" data-id=\"1384018244\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">LuisPinaPhotogrpahy/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Energias de Portugal, or EDP S.A. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EDPFY\" title=\"EDP, S.A.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:EDPFY</a>), remains our preferred utilities pick in Europe, and with the recent pullback in price it continues to be relatively undervalued as we commented in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4689000-energias-de-portugal-focus-deleveraging-could-benefit-stock-price\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4689000-energias-de-portugal-focus-deleveraging-could-benefit-stock-price\" target=\"_blank\">our last article</a>. We do think some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741801-energias-de-portugal-still-left-behind", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:55:27"}, {"id": "4741819", "title": "Leverage And Speculation Are At Extremes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Currency and Exchange Stock Chart for Finance and Economy Display\" data-id=\"1358927461\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cemagraphics</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Financial markets often move in cycles where enthusiasm drives prices higher, sometimes far beyond what fundamentals justify. As discussed in last week\u2019s <strong><em><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741307-extreme-speculation-has-returned\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener noopener noopener\">#BullBearReport</a></em></strong>, leverage and speculation are at the heart of many such cycles. These two powerful forces support</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741819-leverage-speculation-at-extremes", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:46:00"}, {"id": "4741812", "title": "Core & Main, Inc. 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Core &amp; Main, Inc. in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106008\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741812-core-and-main-inc-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:32:01"}, {"id": "4741794", "title": "Lindblad Expeditions: Upbeat Earnings Momentum, But A Moderate Overvaluation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Overview of large cruise ship sailing through icy waters\" data-id=\"148329826\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">goinyk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Lindblad Expeditions Holdings, Inc. </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LIND\" title=\"Lindblad Expeditions Holdings, Inc.\">LIND</a></span>), the expedition ship and land-based experience operator with an extensive partnership with National Geographic, reported very strong Q3 results on the 5<sup>th</sup> of November. The report showed solid earnings, and on top, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741794-lindblad-expeditions-stock-upbeat-earnings-momentum-but-moderate-overvaluation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:29:47"}, {"id": "4741792", "title": "Intel: Challenges For The New CEOs", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Corporation semiconductor company\" data-id=\"1729780233\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tupungato</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>INTC stock: Previous thesis and new development</h2> <p>I last wrote on Intel stock (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) back in mid October 2024. To be more explicit, that article was titled \"Intel: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4727170-intel-inventory-does-not-lie\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4727170-intel-inventory-does-not-lie\" target=\"_blank\">Inventory Does Not Lie</a>.\" That article rated the stock as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741792-intel-challenges-for-new-ceos", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:23:30"}, {"id": "4741791", "title": "Stellantis Needs To Put America First - A Tough Sell To Its European Shareholders", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stellantis Indiana Transmission plant. The Stellantis subsidiaries of FCA are Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, and Ram.\" data-id=\"1393996485\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Stellantis N.V. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STLA\" title=\"Stellantis N.V.\">STLA</a></span>) is currently valued at approximately $38 billion, despite holding $42 billion in cash and having a net positive debt position of roughly $8 billion. At first glance, this valuation appears disconnected from its financial strength.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393996485/image_1393996485.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741791-stellantis-needs-to-put-america-first-a-tough-sell-to-its-european-shareholders", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:18:25"}, {"id": "4741802", "title": "Taking A Defensive Stance On Defense Stocks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"F-15 Eagle Fighter Plane at sunset\" data-id=\"1176850442\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1077px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">guvendemir</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amidst widespread speculation, the return of President Trump as commander-in-chief could threaten earnings growth in the defense industry in 2025. Analysts seeing it this way point to these items on the perceived Trump agenda:</p> <ul> <li>Hardball negotiations with defense</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741802-taking-defensive-stance-on-defense-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:15:00"}, {"id": "4741789", "title": "Celsius Is Not A Bargain Despite 70% Share Price Drop", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man giving energy drink to tired young woman sitting at gym\" data-id=\"1705909279\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">The Good Brigade/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Celsius Holdings, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CELH\" title=\"Celsius Holdings, Inc.\">CELH</a></span>) operates in the Beverages industry, specifically focusing on functional energy drinks and liquid supplements. Celsius has grown significantly, with a total revenue of $1.37 billion TTM and an outstanding 10-year CAGR of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741789-celsius-is-not-a-bargain-despite-70-percent-share-price-drop", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:06:34"}]}